type: software
title: "AEP-Media: Reusable Research Software for Offline Validation of Time-Aware Media Evidence Bundles"
abstract: "Reusable research software for local validation of time-aware media evidence bundles, including profiles, schemas, CLI validators, offline bundle verification, strict declared time-trace validation, adapter-only ingestion, and reproducible evaluation matrices."
